  "text": "Jo Malone London Sakura Cherry Blossom Cologne With Mother’s Day come those baby pink buds, popping up on the limbs of many a cherry tree. This cologne pays homage to the blooms’ seasonality with its limited-edition pink bottle and a sparkling, uplifting scent. If she finds peace in the outdoors, whether in her garden or while enjoying a picnic in the park, this may become her new signature. An airy bergamot note floats over a heart of cherry blossoms, grounded by a smooth rosewood base. Sweet but not too sweet, delicate yet strong—remind you of anyone?Creed Eladaria Eau de ParfumCrafted with not one but three different roses, Eladaria calls to mind a garden under an early-morning mist, enhanced by heady peony and lily-of-the-valley. As it wears, the florals settle into a powdery, nostalgic cloud of cashmere woods and musk, making this scent a welcome choice for moms who love a floral fragrance as much as they do reminiscing with you over a box of childhood photos.Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowMaison Francis Kurkdjian Kurky Eau de ParfumA waft of tutti-frutti candy hits the nose first, before this fragrance dries down to a cocoon of musk cradled by facets of vanilla and sandalwood. It’s sunny, whimsical, and warm, meant to evoke memories of perfumer Francis Kurkdjian’s childhood—and perfect for the mom who’s never stopped nurturing her own inner child.Christian Louboutin Fétiche La Rose Eau de ParfumA scent as seductive as the heel that inspired it, Fétiche La Rose centers around an addictive rose note sidled up against a boozy black-cherry accord. We’d pick this Nordstrom-exclusive release for a confident mom friend who still prioritizes fun nights out; notes of ginger and pink pepper give it an unexpected kick she’ll love.Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowYves Saint Laurent Libre L’eau Nue A mom with an infectious sense of energy and adventure will instantly gravitate to this vibrant citrus scent. L’Eau Nue uses oil-in-water technology for an alcohol-free parfum that mimics the juiciness of a ripe mandarin orange, the faintly floral notes of a trailing orange blossom, and the aromatic effect of freshly picked lavender. Housed in a white, jewel-like bottle, the liquid leaves a luminous glow wherever it is sprayed, making it a multisensory pleasure to apply. BYREDO Blanche Absolu de ParfumBlanche Absolu takes BYREDO’s original Blanche and pushes it to new depths, with sparkling aldehydes, pronounced florals and musks, and as the pièce de résistance, a crack of black pepper at the top. The fluttering floral notes—composed of neroli, rose absolute, violet, and watery jasmine—pair with aldehydes for a “freshly washed sheets” vibe, while black pepper and a musky base add a cozy crispness. The mom who swears by a starched button-down and loves the smell of clean laundry won’t be able to put this one down.Advertisement - Continue Reading BelowParfums de Marly Valaya Exclusif Eau de ParfumShe’s feminine, elegant, and prioritizes self-care over everything. Her collection of loungewear is just as noteworthy as the rest of her wardrobe, and she always keeps a fresh bouquet of flowers in her home. If this sounds like a mom you know, gift her Valaya Exclusif this year. Top notes of almond, bergamot, and lemon rest on a bed of orange blossom, white flowers, and creamy musks for a scent that radiates comfort and quiet luxury.Bulgari Eau Parfumée Thé Vert Eau de ToiletteEau Parfumée Thé Vert was originally launched in 1992, when it was distributed among only the top clients of Bulgari fragrances. Now the brand has reintroduced the scent as a Nordstrom exclusive, with an energizing, grassy heart complemented by mandarin, neroli, and refreshing green-tea leaves. The mom who loves green scents or is looking to add more serenity to her life will be impressed by the bottle’s label, too, which features hand-drawn illustrations from a French botanist made specifically for Bulgari.",
