ly gravitate to this vibrant citrus scent. L’Eau Nue uses oil-in-water technology for an alcohol-free parfum that mimics the juiciness of a ripe mandarin orange, the faintly floral notes of a trailing orange blossom, and the aromatic effect of freshly picked lavender. Housed in a white, jewel-like bottle, the liquid leaves a luminous glow wherever it is sprayed, making it a multisensory pleasure to apply. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-ad-exclude=\"(min-width: 90rem)\" data-embed=\"embed-product\" data-theme-key=\"listicle-slide-inner-container\" size=\"large\" data-journey-content=\"true\" id=\"slide-6\" data-anchor-id=\"slide-6\" data-journey-listicle-slide=\"true\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-theme-key=\"embedded-product-info\" size=\"large\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2\u003eBYREDO Blanche Absolu de Parfum\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-theme-key=\"base-link\" href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/s/byredo-blanche-absolu-50ml/8217845?campaign=na\u0026amp;utm_source=hearst\u0026amp;utm_medium=display_agency\u0026amp;utm_campaign=4613_j013086_24386\u0026amp;utm_term=hearst_display_agency\u0026amp;utm_channel=up_nd_display\u0026amp;utm_content=na\" aria-label=\"$280 at Nordstrom for Blanche Absolu de Parfum\" data-href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/s/byredo-blanche-absolu-50ml/8217845?campaign=na\u0026amp;utm_source=hearst\u0026amp;utm_medium=display_agency\u0026amp;utm_campaign=4613_j013086_24386\u0026amp;utm_term=hearst_display_agency\u0026amp;utm_channel=up_nd_display\u0026amp;utm_content=na\" data-product-url=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/s/byredo-blanche-absolu-50ml/8217845?campaign=na\u0026amp;utm_source=hearst\u0026amp;utm_medium=display_agency\u0026amp;utm_campaign=4613_j013086_24386\u0026amp;utm_term=hearst_display_agency\u0026amp;utm_channel=up_nd_display\u0026amp;utm_content=na\" data-affiliate=\"false\" data-affiliate-url=\"\" data-affiliate-network=\"\" data-vars-ga-call-to-action=\"$280 at Nordstrom\" d